Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.17,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,まりなを返してください
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.60,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,どこの誰だか存じませんが
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.99,0:23:02.46,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,まりなは　おなかを痛めて産んだ　大切な娘なんです
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.53,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,まりちゃん　ごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.54,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,いいママじゃなかったよね
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.54,0:23:12.51,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,でも　大好きだからお願い
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.19,0:23:15.79,JP - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,帰ってきて
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.47,0:23:24.84,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃんはしずかちゃんにひどいことをする
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.92,0:23:26.66,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.88,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃん　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:02.84,0:24:05.88,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃんのパパとママ
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.79,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃんじゃなくてごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.33,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,一緒にいられなくしてごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.66,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,まりなちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.84,0:24:23.81,JP - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,殺して　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:24:28.62,0:24:30.15,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,考えなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:24:31.58,0:24:35.41,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,ぼくは何をしちゃったのか　どうすればよかったのか
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.80,0:24:37.00,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚ピー
Dialogue: 1,0:24:37.90,0:24:40.21,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,これからどうすればいいのか
Dialogue: 1,0:24:40.21,0:24:41.37,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章魚ピー
Dialogue: 1,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.70,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,ありがとう　章魚ピー
Dialogue: 1,0:24:49.77,0:24:51.42,JP - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,殺してくれて
Dialogue: 1,0:24:56.52,0:24:57.80,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,それで
Dialogue: 1,0:24:58.62,0:25:02.76,JP - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,しずかちゃんともう一度　お話ししなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.74,0:25:12.11,JP - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,おーい　こっち何かあるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:25:12.11,0:25:14.12,JP - down,Staff B,0,0,0,,おいおい　これ何
Dialogue: 1,0:25:14.12,0:25:15.91,JP - down,Staff C,0,0,0,,えっ　何　何
Dialogue: 1,0:25:16.34,0:25:18.99,JP - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,えっ　ヤバくねこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:25:20.33,0:25:21.60,JP - down,Staff A,0,0,0,,子供
Comment: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.63,CN - down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.23,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我很担心你就跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.14,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.02,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.97,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,什么东西 好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:27.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.80,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊 说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.22,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.65,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.73,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,因为章鱼噼的魔法 麻里奈死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 静香那不是魔法是快乐道具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.82,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,啊 章鱼噼是从快乐星球来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.62,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我是快乐星人噼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.86,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,记得 是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.68,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,快乐果实很好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:05.74,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.83,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不对 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.71,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.51,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:19.56,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,「什么」奇怪 意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.88,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,为什么要杀了她 明明有其它的办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.50,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是麻里奈她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.38,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,而且你为什么 若无其事地扔下她就走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.47,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你应该知道会惹出麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:37.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,东 东君 感觉你好恐怖噼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.55,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,要更加开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.56,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,章鱼 有「人」可是死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.69,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你什么说话方式 搞什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:46.99,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,你先闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是 麻里奈是因为魔法而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.21,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.00,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,魔法什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.88,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,先 先不管是魔法还是什么 杀了人就是杀了人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:09.02,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世 我认为你会进少管所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.38,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:16.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,「这是外星人做的」解释根本行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.49,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那我就不能去见恰噼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.41,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我在书上读到过 要想减轻罪行只能自首
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.15,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,马上去警局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.31,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,还有其它的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.43,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,其它的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.43,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,自首以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我不是很懂书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.55,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君你挺了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:47.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,在小说里 有把罪名嫁祸给他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.77,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不对 那是虚构的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.18,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,常见的是把犯罪隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,算是基本的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.19,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.34,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那 就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.55,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.02,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:09.13,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我不想进少管所 那就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.67,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那个 要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊 不对 那也是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.00,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,再说了只靠小孩子如何隐藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.04,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,有章鱼噼的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:27.06,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以 东君能不能帮我想个办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.12,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,这种事情我怎么可能做得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:29.76,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.42,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,为什么做不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.76,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,只有我们两个的话 肯定很快就会被捉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:41.18,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,所以我希望东君你能帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.99,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我既没有朋友 也不能依靠妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.19,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,其他人也不能依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.20,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.98,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,哥哥明明就能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.15,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.30,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,除你之外就没有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.22,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我的话 能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.12,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.50,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,「少管所」是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.01,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,喂 章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.06,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.49,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.57,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 那个是「记忆盒子」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.19,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我不是问名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.95,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,放进去的东西能够保持原有的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.83,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,比如说漂亮的叶子之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.46,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,它还能改变大小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:41.96,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:56.06,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,总之先把云母坂埋起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.54,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,凶器就藏在章鱼的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.24,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,还有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.57,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.82,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,这样真的没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.74,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼 变身调色盘的伪装可是很完美的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.74,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.57,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那行 我去拿铲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.20,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,千万不要被家里人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.77,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,否则 全部功夫都白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.63,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.86,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.01,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.45,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,这样真的可以吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.09,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 我今后以麻里奈的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:41.04,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,还有把麻里奈藏起来 这些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.62,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.60,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,章鱼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.50,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你这种说话方式 会暴露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.64,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我会做好的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.59,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你又这么说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,只要静香能笑出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.13,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我今后会以麻里奈的身份加油努力的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.38,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,像麻里奈一样活蹦乱跳 我会努力扮演的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.23,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:01.23,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.90,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,结穗是什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.04,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,窗帘 装窗帘上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.61,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,用别人赚的钱净买些破烂玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.69,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,你个寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.33,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.94,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,那 那经常去夜总会的你算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.74,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,那是我 自己辛苦赚的血汗钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.66,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,我爱怎么花我就怎么花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.75,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊 我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:22.82,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:32.33,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,要是打到眼睛可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.90,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,她是女孩要是在脸上留了疤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.22,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,都说了 根本没受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.46,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,麻里奈也说自己没事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:43.90,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里奈还能问你要点医药费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:48.14,CN - down,Mairna's dad,0,0,0,,成天妄想被害 有完没完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:51.44,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,所以我才受不了你这样毫不工作的废物女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.33,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}好过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.65,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈的爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:58.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,每天说好多话 关系非常好呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.36,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是为了麻里奈和你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.57,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}为家庭尽心尽责牺牲奉献
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.66,CN - up,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,{\an8}别好像我们欠了你恩情似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.16,CN - up,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,{\an8}你成天哭能解决问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.16,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.16,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,那么 我们去找恰噼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.50,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,啊 不错呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:10.08,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不行的说 都说了现在不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.74,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,恰噼在你父亲住的地方 那可是东京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.83,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,小孩子自己去太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.38,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.85,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我们得等到这只章鱼融进她家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.41,CN - up,Maripi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.11,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,说起来「离婚调停」是什么呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.64,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈妈妈一直都在说的噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.76,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那边的我已经埋好了应该没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.81,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但我们应该暂时离开城镇一段时间避嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.19,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,从现在开始仔细制定计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.04,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,执行就放在暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,在那之前要每天放学后开作战会议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.49,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.29,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不对不对 我明明没时间做些事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.03,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,今天得赶紧回家好好学习才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:10:59.92,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.35,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,在外面玩耍挺少见的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.89,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.39,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,是班里的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:07.52,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,润也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.82,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,你这家伙 还真不叫我「哥哥」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.49,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,你是东君的哥哥吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.58,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,噼 嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:19.65,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,润 润也才是你回来挺早的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:23.11,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,啊没有 接下来我要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.32,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,妈妈那边你帮我去哄哄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.55,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.89,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:36.37,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,润也他 实际上没有打工的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.39,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,多少零花钱他要都能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.16,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,但却总是让妈妈她担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.63,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,是 是吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,还擅自用自己赚的钱买了那傻缺的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.35,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明只需要好好学习就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.82,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明比起任何人 都更加备受期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.53,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.90,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,拿走它不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.40,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.37,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:08.49,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,这样的话 那个人肯定会因震惊而辞去工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:12.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,不行 他恐怕是不会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.67,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,再说了 那可是盗窃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.12,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.01,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我认为东君你 能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:32.11,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这里就是东君的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.67,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以 要拿走什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.48,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,笨蛋 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.79,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,万一发生意外 有章鱼噼的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.72,CN - down,Maripi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:45.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,虽这么说 但带这种家伙回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.32,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,总感觉很开心呢噼 东君 噼噼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.37,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.07,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,润也只有在洗澡的时候才会摘下戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.84,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,现在进入他的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:00.51,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.31,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好了呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.86,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,好 只要把它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.31,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.60,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我终于买到了 和女朋友一对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:16.05,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,果然这种东西 用自己的钱买才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.42,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,他到底在装什么正常人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:25.26,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,明明想要的东西 无论什么都能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:29.69,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,对了 你用的那个很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.69,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,下次等打工钱入账 我也给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.62,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,被发现了会生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.92,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,喂 你就没有道具想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.98,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我不知道噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.92,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,也 也不是那个  噼 也不是这个噼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.09,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.64,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,手机 手机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.64,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,窗户 我有打开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.86,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,差点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.22,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,要被发现就惨了 快逃 章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 东君 来这里噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.01,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:27.17,CN - down,Announcement,0,0,0,,重量超过 重量超过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.25,CN - down,Announcement,0,0,0,,电池没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.89,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.80,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.42,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,我记得听到了啥声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:41.95,CN - down,Junya,0,0,0,,是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.34,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.04,CN - down,Announcement,0,0,0,,重量超过 重量超过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.83,CN - up,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.75,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.96,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 噼 噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.14,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,东君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:07.97,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,你没事吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:16.53,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.68,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,有没有哪里会痛呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.69,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.11,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这样啊噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:23.93,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.56,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好了噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:36.12,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊 但是 戒指没有拿走呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.22,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,我做不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.20,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.13,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,那么 需要惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.59,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,松饼点心就不给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.04,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.05,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,你哥哥一直都是满分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.47,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,你可以忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.05,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.41,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那就 下次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.55,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,下次的我 会更加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:03.66,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,啊啊 又没得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.39,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,难得我今天给你做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:10.63,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,对不起 今天我会忍耐的 下次肯定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.06,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.16,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,这些努力全都没什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.36,CN - down,Azuma's mom,0,0,0,,不管你做什么 都还是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.53,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.51,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.69,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,请不要 对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.57,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你们两人怎么了 破烂不堪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,很破破烂烂吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.36,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.60,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,上次在东君家 发现了一个糟糕的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:27.44,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.23,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,拍拍翅膀承受不了人类的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:35.30,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,所以没办法飞到恰噼所在的东京噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:39.43,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,无所谓 我从来没有期待过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.02,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,是吗噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.68,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那么 只有船和新干线了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.39,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.32,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,剩下的 就只是钱的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.19,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:52.72,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,呐 为什么快乐道具这么没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.53,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.66,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,就这水平还来地球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.87,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,才没有这回事噼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.73,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,在快乐星球上有更多的快乐道具噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.59,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,像是土星狗立体模型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.82,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,乐色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.04,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,还有「大快乐时钟」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.88,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,这个可是随时都能穿越时空的好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,那现在赶紧把它拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.21,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,全部都修改为一切没发生不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.26,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,噼 这是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.58,CN - up,Azuma,0,0,0,,你这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:24.05,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,因为 我现在回不了快乐星球噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.44,CN - up,Shizuka,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.94,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,久世 我们去东京搭乘新干线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.08,CN - down,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯 那就 来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:32.75,CN - down,Azuma,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:38.22,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,三人在一起的时候很快乐呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.16,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,静香能够快乐笑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.78,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,真希望 能一直这样生活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.79,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,啊嘞 但是 说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.25,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,为什么我不能回去快乐星球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:58.04,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,到最后你连咱妈的六十岁寿宴都没露面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:57.52,CN - up,MariPi,0,0,0,,嗯 完全没头绪噼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:01.28,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,那是因为我也有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.60,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,就只是赚不了钱的家庭主妇教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.85,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.98,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,总是去夜总会有家也不回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.93,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,那我用自己赚的钱去喝酒什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:13.94,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,你对自家人的亲戚就这冷漠态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.39,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,是吧 麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.89,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,唔 什么呢噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:21.52,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里 你又这样说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.94,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,是学校现在流行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.83,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,麻里奈最近变得开朗起来挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.60,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,反观你妈 还是唠唠叨叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.39,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,麻里奈 你要不来爸爸这边吧
