Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:40.72,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:44.43,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,那是不是东京 是恰噼在的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.13,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我要去噼 爸爸那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.02,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,哦 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:54.79,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,那么 麻里奈也来爸爸这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.57,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,噼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.91,CN - down,Marina's dad,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 你要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.41,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.83,CN - down,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,麻里
