Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.28,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.15,CN - up,Marina's mom,0,0,0,,你那种说话方式怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.04,CN - down,Takopoi,0,0,0,,得告诉东君
