Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:12.51,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,但是 我一直会爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:15.79,CN - down,Marina's mother,0,0,0,,请你回来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:24.84,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,麻里奈对静香做了很过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:26.66,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,但是
