Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:05.88,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈的爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.79,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我不是真正的麻里奈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:12.33,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我无法让你们团圆 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.66,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:23.81,CN - down,MariPi,0,0,0,,我杀了你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:30.15,CN - down,Takopi,0,0,0,,我要思考
